14
00:02:54,570 --> 00:02:56,780
Brother Yang, come eat.

15
00:03:20,390 --> 00:03:21,900
Sit.

16
00:03:24,070 --> 00:03:25,980
Thank you, Yayun.

17
00:03:26,740 --> 00:03:28,360
