18
00:03:28,360 --> 00:03:31,850
Consider today as me coming to warm the house up.

19
00:03:33,460 --> 00:03:35,190
Oh right!

20
00:03:38,780 --> 00:03:40,830
There's something good.

21
00:03:46,750 --> 00:03:49,980
- Little potatoes again? 
 - I specially roasted them for you.

22
00:03:50,750 --> 00:03:54,370
Yayun, you treat me so well.

23
00:03:54,370 --> 00:03:58,240
Brother Yang, I want to treat you well for my whole life.

24
00:04:13,400 --> 00:04:15,290
- Hello? 
 - Hello.

25
00:04:15,290 --> 00:04:17,710
Do you need a loan?

26
