37
00:08:18,360 --> 00:08:21,300
Is it that Xiao Wei from work?

38
00:08:21,300 --> 00:08:23,720
Mom, you know?

39
00:08:25,220 --> 00:08:29,180
You... tell Yang to answer the phone. I'll scold him.

40
00:08:30,460 --> 00:08:34,970
