41
00:08:36,470 --> 00:08:39,930
Yang really has no conscience.

42
00:08:39,930 --> 00:08:43,590
Zhizhi, don't worry. Mom is definitely on your side.

43
00:08:43,590 --> 00:08:47,940
I'll get him to break up with that girl immediately and come home to apologize to you.

44
00:08:50,070 --> 00:08:51,590
Mom,

45
00:08:52,630 --> 00:08:54,950
you're so sensible.

46
00:08:55,740 --> 00:08:59,670
Zhizhi,  but I-I have to advise you.

47
00:08:59,670 --> 00:09:03,190
When he gets home, don't argue or bother him;

48
00:09:03,190 --> 00:09:07,330
or else, he'll run back to her when she waves her hand.

49
00:09:07,330 --> 00:09:09,240
Do you hear?

50
00:09:15,100 --> 00:09:17,890
Okay. I'll listen to you.

51
00:09:17,890 --> 00:09:22,690
Okay. Then I'm hanging up now.

52
00:09:34,650 --> 00:09:37,890
Are you stupid? If you lose Zhizhi,

53
00:09:37,890 --> 00:09:39,960
 you will regret it in the future.

54
00:09:39,960 --> 00:09:41,800
I know how to take care of this problem.

55
00:09:41,800 --> 00:09:45,360
You brat, if you don't listen to me, then you're not my son anymore.

56
00:09:45,360 --> 00:09:47,410
Mom.

57
00:09:47,410 --> 00:09:49,570
Today, go back home.

58
00:09:53,560 --> 00:09:55,420
- But Zhizhi— 
 - Yang,

59
00:09:55,420 --> 00:09:58,530
Zhizhi already promised me that as long as you go home,

60
00:09:58,530 --> 00:10:00,190
 this problem will be left in the past.

61
00:10:00,190 --> 00:10:03,460
She won't make it difficult for you anymore.

62
00:10:03,460 --> 00:10:05,260
- I'll think about it. 
 - Think about what?

63
00:10:05,260 --> 00:10:07,360
What is there to think about? That is how it is going to be.

64
00:10:07,360 --> 00:10:10,290
Okay. I've still have work to do. I'm going to get back to work.

65
