Okay, okay, okay.

68
00:11:27,140 --> 00:11:29,880
- All right, all right, all right. 
 - Come on, come on, come on.

69
00:11:29,880 --> 00:11:31,380
Up you go.

70
00:11:31,380 --> 00:11:34,540
I still want to play! Woah!

71
00:11:34,540 --> 00:11:37,220
Come up. One.

72
00:11:38,850 --> 00:11:42,040
How about we take a break? Aunt is already tired.

73
00:11:42,040 --> 00:11:43,590
I still want to play!

74
00:11:43,590 --> 00:11:47,400
Zhizhi, Yang really wants to go home.

75
00:11:47,400 --> 00:11:51,600
He also acknowledges his wrongdoings and promised not to do it again.

76
00:11:51,600 --> 00:11:52,780
Really?

77
00:11:52,780 --> 00:11:55,270
He told me himself.

78
00:11:56,980 --> 00:12:02,620
But he still hasn't... called me or messaged me.

79
00:12:02,620 --> 00:12:07,070
Men, they admit their faults in their heart, but they still want to save face.

80
00:12:07,070 --> 00:12:10,570
Zhizhi, how about you take some initiative?

81
00:12:10,570 --> 00:12:15,200
Call him or pick him up from work.

82
00:12:22,370 --> 00:12:25,340
- Are you tired? 
 - Yes.

83
00:12:25,340 --> 00:12:29,080
Taking care of a child is too exhausting. It's really not easy.

84
00:12:29,860 --> 00:12:32,960
I'm also tired.

85
00:12:32,960 --> 00:12:35,630
What do you have to be tired of?

86
00:12:35,630 --> 00:12:40,870
I have to fight against gravity and age. Do you think that's easy?

87
00:12:40,870 --> 00:12:44,300
Then, do you think you can win against gravity and age?

88
00:12:44,300 --> 00:12:49,080
Even though I can't win, I still need to fight until the very end.

89
00:12:49,080 --> 00:12:50,600
I'm too lazy to care about you.

90
