What did she say?

92
00:13:17,930 --> 00:13:20,770
Can you guys help me find out

93
00:13:20,770 --> 00:13:23,320
where Liu Yang is living right now?

94
00:13:26,480 --> 00:13:28,490
What do you want to do?

95
00:13:30,270 --> 00:13:32,940
I want to give him an opportunity to get out of this.

96
00:13:33,650 --> 00:13:36,380
Did he personally admit his wrongs to you?

97
00:13:38,310 --> 00:13:40,340
He did to his mom.

98
00:13:40,340 --> 00:13:45,650
Besides, I am also partially at fault.

99
00:13:46,740 --> 00:13:49,090
Can you really forgive him?

100
00:13:52,530 --> 00:13:55,030
I'm willing to forgive him

101
00:13:55,970 --> 00:13:58,220
for Yuwei's sake.

102
00:13:58,220 --> 00:13:59,970
That's fine.

103
00:14:15,000 --> 00:14:18,220
One, two, three.

104
00:14:18,220 --> 00:14:19,210
Okay.

105
00:14:19,210 --> 00:14:20,500
Does it look good?

106
00:14:20,500 --> 00:14:22,820
Yes.

107
00:14:22,820 --> 00:14:24,420
Hey, what do you want to do this weekend?

108
00:14:24,420 --> 00:14:25,660
Whatever you want.

109
00:14:25,660 --> 00:14:29,380
Then, how about we invite your parents to eat a meal with us?

110
00:14:29,380 --> 00:14:32,630
They have plans this weekend. They'll be away.

111
00:14:32,630 --> 00:14:34,970
Last time I wanted to invite them, they were in Europe.

112
00:14:34,970 --> 00:14:38,120
The time before that, they went to Thailand. The time even before that—

113
00:14:38,120 --> 00:14:42,510
Xiaoling, I just think the time is not right yet.

114
00:14:42,510 --> 00:14:44,810
Then, when will the time be right?

115
00:14:44,810 --> 00:14:47,830
Do you know that according to my family's traditions,

116
00:14:47,830 --> 00:14:51,670
if you meet my parents, it means we are about to get married?

117
00:14:51,670 --> 00:14:54,690
You mean, you are not ready to get married to me?

118
00:14:54,690 --> 00:14:58,690
I just think that we're not at that age yet.

119
00:14:58,690 --> 00:15:00,570
Got it.

120
00:15:00,570 --> 00:15:03,560
I actually really like how we are right now.

121
00:15:03,560 --> 00:15:07,300
We have the sweetness of love, but not the triviality of marriage.

122
00:15:08,430 --> 00:15:10,120
Then aren't you afraid that I'll run away with someone else?

123
00:15:10,120 --> 00:15:11,740
I am.

124
00:15:14,630 --> 00:15:16,580
But I know...

125
00:15:17,490 --> 00:15:19,390
you won't.

126
00:15:43,060 --> 00:15:44,270
I'm coming.

127
00:15:44,270 --> 00:15:45,860
So fast?

128
00:15:45,860 --> 00:15:48,600
I just placed the order, is it already here?

129
00:15:52,650 --> 00:15:54,420
I'm coming, I'm coming.

130
00:15:57,240 --> 00:15:59,430
Xiaoling?

131
00:16:00,320 --> 00:16:02,680
Wait a minute!

132
00:16:02,680 --> 00:16:05,710
Li Haowen, what are you doing? Did you hide a man in there?

133
00:16:05,710 --> 00:16:09,190
I'm changing clothes, I'll be ready soon.

134
00:16:09,190 --> 00:16:12,160
Open the door! If you don't, I'm leaving!

135
00:16:12,160 --> 00:16:14,270
Coming, coming, coming.

136
00:16:22,570 --> 00:16:24,200
Please come in.

137
00:16:41,050 --> 00:16:43,380
How do you know where I live?

138
00:16:44,950 --> 00:16:47,450
Figuring out where your home is, isn't that easy?

139
00:16:49,640 --> 00:16:51,570
Help me with something.

140
00:16:52,410 --> 00:16:56,340
Didn't you say that you wouldn't come looking for me even if you were dying?

141
00:16:58,180 --> 00:16:59,580
Let go.

142
00:16:59,580 --> 00:17:03,450
I was just kidding. I'm very happy you came.

143
00:17:03,450 --> 00:17:06,970
Sit, sit, sit.

144
00:17:08,900 --> 00:17:10,750
Drink some orange juice.

145
00:17:12,970 --> 00:17:14,870
Open it.

146
00:17:19,020 --> 00:17:22,320
You hurt me so deeply,

147
00:17:22,320 --> 00:17:24,810
can't I just talk about it a bit?

148
00:17:26,150 --> 00:17:28,130
Tell me. What do you want me to do?

149
00:17:28,130 --> 00:17:32,020
Not just one thing, but eight or ten things, as long as I can do it,

150
00:17:32,020 --> 00:17:34,900
I will go through fire and water and will not refuse under any circumstances!

151
00:17:35,950 --> 00:17:37,800
Be my ex-boyfriend.

152
00:17:38,910 --> 00:17:40,660
What did you say?

153
00:17:41,680 --> 00:17:45,030
Be my ex-boyfriend.

154
00:17:45,650 --> 00:17:50,050
I've never even been your boyfriend, how can I be your ex-boyfriend?

155
00:17:50,050 --> 00:17:52,270
Are you going to help me or not?

156
00:17:52,270 --> 00:17:54,160
Forgive me for I cannot comply with your wishes.

157
00:18:01,420 --> 00:18:05,920
Can you just let me be your current boyfriend for a while?

158
00:18:08,610 --> 00:18:11,060
Current boyfriend?

159
00:18:20,730 --> 00:18:22,940
Be more gentle!

160
00:18:22,940 --> 00:18:25,680
Ow, ow, ow.

161
00:18:25,680 --> 00:18:27,190
Will you help me or not?

162
00:18:27,190 --> 00:18:29,470
Help, help, I'll help.

163
00:18:30,090 --> 00:18:32,480
You really hurt me.

164
00:18:32,480 --> 00:18:36,920
Remember. You have to strictly follow my plan.

165
00:18:37,510 --> 00:18:39,410
What plan?

166
00:18:40,240 --> 00:18:43,470
First: drive that roaster sports car of yours.

167
00:18:43,470 --> 00:18:46,730
You must figure out where the car roof switch is this time.

168
00:18:46,730 --> 00:18:47,960
Second:

169
00:18:47,960 --> 00:18:52,770
rush to me with a ring and flowers to propose.

170
00:18:52,770 --> 00:18:56,020
This way, Wei Shang will surely get jealous.

171
00:18:56,020 --> 00:18:59,580
Then seize this opportunity to provoke him, to force him to propose to me.

172
00:19:09,860 --> 00:19:11,530
Do you understand?

173
00:19:14,970 --> 00:19:16,990
I understand very well.

174
00:19:16,990 --> 00:19:18,300
Then I'll go set up a time.

175
00:19:18,300 --> 00:19:20,490
Don't be so impatient.

176
00:19:22,540 --> 00:19:24,200
I have to think about this.

177
00:19:24,200 --> 00:19:26,200
What do you have to think about?

178
00:19:26,200 --> 00:19:30,220
This character is so important. I have to think about how to be immersed in the role.

179
00:20:28,670 --> 00:20:30,330
Thank you.

180
00:20:35,500 --> 00:20:39,100
- What are you looking at? 
 - Nothing.

181
00:20:39,100 --> 00:20:40,840
Let me look at the menu.

182
00:20:40,840 --> 00:20:43,610
You look and tell me if you want to eat anything else.

183
00:20:56,280 --> 00:20:59,260
Where are you? What is going on?

184
00:21:01,730 --> 00:21:04,900
Are you still not done looking?

185
00:21:04,900 --> 00:21:09,590
I'm giving you five minutes to get here; or else, never show up in my life again!

186
00:21:41,670 --> 00:21:43,240
Xiaoling.

187
00:21:45,300 --> 00:21:47,170
Xiaoling.

188
00:21:47,170 --> 00:21:48,950
That man is calling you.

189
00:21:48,950 --> 00:21:51,200
Really?

190
00:21:55,350 --> 00:21:57,000
Gu Xiaoling.

191
00:22:03,020 --> 00:22:07,050
I'm begging you. Give me another chance.

192
00:22:08,330 --> 00:22:10,940
Lei Haowen, get up.

193
00:22:10,940 --> 00:22:13,030
If you don't say yes, I won't get up.

194
00:22:13,030 --> 00:22:15,090
We already broke up!

195
00:22:15,090 --> 00:22:18,280
But my world can't be without you, Gu Xiaoling.

196
00:22:21,190 --> 00:22:23,960
Gu Xiaoling, marry me!

197
00:22:23,960 --> 00:22:27,320
This is not possible! I already have a boyfriend.

198
00:22:27,320 --> 00:22:29,800
It's fine. That's not important.

199
00:22:29,800 --> 00:22:34,310
As long as you haven't gotten married, then I still have an opportunity, Xiaoling.

200
00:22:34,310 --> 00:22:37,260
I can give you whatever you want. I can buy you purses,

201
00:22:37,260 --> 00:22:39,710
lipsticks, big villas,

202
00:22:39,710 --> 00:22:43,650
sports cars. As long as you want them, I can give them all to you. Xiaoling, marry me!

203
00:22:43,650 --> 00:22:46,760
I can give you happiness Xiaoling!

204
00:22:47,340 --> 00:22:51,530
This is my fiancé. We're going to get married very soon.

205
00:22:59,080 --> 00:23:00,890
Impossible.

206
00:23:00,890 --> 00:23:03,430
That's impossible. That is just your excuse, right?

207
00:23:03,430 --> 00:23:06,110
- Marry me, Xiaoling. 
 - Bro.

208
00:23:16,650 --> 00:23:18,770
Come on, get up.

209
00:23:22,820 --> 00:23:25,420
The second you came in, you made a huge mistake.

210
00:23:25,420 --> 00:23:27,460
Proposals are huge things.

211
00:23:27,460 --> 00:23:29,620
Look at you, dressed all disorderly.

212
00:23:29,620 --> 00:23:32,160
You look like you're fleeing from famine.

213
00:23:37,660 --> 00:23:41,510
Also, these flowers. From these flowers, I can see

214
00:23:41,510 --> 00:23:44,190
that you have already put a lot of heart into them.

215
00:23:44,190 --> 00:23:48,160
But you should learn to leave some space, understand?

216
00:23:50,190 --> 00:23:52,600
Also, the way you kneeled.

217
00:23:52,600 --> 00:23:56,550
You're proposing, not praying during Happy New Year. You must put only one knee to the ground.

218
00:23:56,550 --> 00:23:58,330
The most important part is

219
00:23:58,330 --> 00:24:02,200
that at this time, purses, lipsticks,

220
00:24:02,200 --> 00:24:05,230
sports cars, and big villas are all useless.

221
00:24:05,230 --> 00:24:08,000
The most important thing is being sincere.

222
00:24:08,870 --> 00:24:11,790
Here. Let me show you an example.

223
00:24:18,330 --> 00:24:20,170
My love,

224
00:24:20,850 --> 00:24:23,140
will you marry me?

225
00:24:30,420 --> 00:24:31,880
I—

226
00:24:31,880 --> 00:24:35,540
Did you see it? You have to do it like this.

227
00:24:35,540 --> 00:24:37,650
Here. You try.

228
00:24:38,490 --> 00:24:42,840
- Me? 
 - Yeah. Take it. Give it a try.

229
00:24:43,930 --> 00:24:47,090
Good luck. I'll help you record this.

230
00:24:47,090 --> 00:24:49,220
Afterward, you can see if you're not happy about anything,

231
00:24:49,220 --> 00:24:51,420
so you can change when you get back.

232
00:25:02,770 --> 00:25:07,090
Nevermind, Xiaoling. It's never too late to propose.

233
00:25:07,090 --> 00:25:09,850
This time, it's my fault that I didn't prepare well.

234
00:25:09,850 --> 00:25:12,450
I'll come back again after more preparation, okay?

235
00:25:28,190 --> 00:25:30,830
You're not mad at all?

236
00:25:32,150 --> 00:25:35,180
Xiaoling, sit and talk.

237
00:25:36,150 --> 00:25:38,500
Sit down to talk.

238
00:25:41,630 --> 00:25:48,450
A man would only be that helpless in front of the woman he loves the most.

239
00:25:48,450 --> 00:25:51,330
Xiaoling, I recommend that

240
00:25:51,330 --> 00:25:54,530
you think about his proposal seriously.

241
00:25:54,530 --> 00:25:56,640
Then, what about us?

242
00:25:57,540 --> 00:25:59,780
We...

243
00:26:01,620 --> 00:26:03,930
I really like you.

244
00:26:05,300 --> 00:26:08,170
But I'm afraid that we can only be boyfriend and girlfriend.

245
00:26:08,170 --> 00:26:10,340
Why?

246
00:26:12,210 --> 00:26:15,870
I'm afraid that my parents won't accept you.

247
00:26:15,870 --> 00:26:19,640
Your parents haven't even met me, why would they reject me?

248
00:26:20,450 --> 00:26:26,160
My parents definitely won't approve of me getting married to a woman that's three years older than me.

249
00:26:27,660 --> 00:26:31,990
Was I only older than you today? What were you doing earlier?

250
00:26:33,000 --> 00:26:35,890
Besides, if you didn't look at my ID, who would know I'm older than you by three years?

251
00:26:35,890 --> 00:26:38,440
My parents can tell.

252
00:26:39,230 --> 00:26:43,310
Xiaoling, as long as we don't talk about getting married,

253
00:26:43,310 --> 00:26:47,350
or meeting parents, we can still continue to date.

254
00:26:50,020 --> 00:26:52,350
Continue my ass!

255
00:27:10,280 --> 00:27:16,050
♫  Summer is hot, the wind blows as usual ♫

256
00:27:16,850 --> 00:27:21,420
♫  Yet you arouse my warmth ♫

257
00:27:25,950 --> 00:27:28,290
I told you earlier on,

258
00:27:28,290 --> 00:27:33,210
that that guy has a face of an asshole. You just didn't believe me.

259
00:27:38,310 --> 00:27:40,960
Don't feel upset.

